data.Name: Dabin
data.Bio: Dabin Lee, Toronto, Canada Dabin grew up playing and performing music all his life. His musical background of blues, indie and folk music influenced the melodic and rhythmic nature of his productions. His first single 'We are the Night' caught the attention of major networks such as Dubstep.net and Vital FM. Since then, his productions have gained support from the likes of Benga, Modestep, Dirtyphonics, Felix Cartal, Dirtyloud, Vaski, The Killabits Read more on Last.fm
